OL,3,CIs the BBC Red Button Text service
OL,4,Cserving a useful purpose?
OL,6,FIt was argued that many who still used
OL,7,Fthe service did not have internet
OL,8,Faccess.
OL,10,FBut now the emergency has passed. Life
OL,11,Fis back to normal.
OL,13,FThere is no original journalism on the
OL,14,FRed Button Text service. Generally it
OL,15,Fis made up of the first four
OL,16,Fparagraphs of stories from the BBC
OL,17,Fwebsite.
OL,19,FSome of them make no sense on the red
OL,20,Fbutton service.
OL,22,FThere was a prime example on Saturday.
