OL,3,CIs the BBC Red Button Text service
OL,4,Cserving a useful purpose?
OL,6,FThe BBC website carried an enjoyable
OL,7,Fpiece looking back at the famous
OL,8,Fmotorway service chain Little Chef. It
OL,9,Fwas featured on the BBC News homepage.
OL,11,FBut on the red button service it
OL,12,Flooked ridiculous.
OL,14,FIt featured as a top headline and the
OL,15,Ffirst four paragraphs in isolation
OL,16,Fdidn't tell a story.
OL,18,FDoes anyone actually look at the
OL,19,Fservice which is being broadcast? Is
OL,20,Fit simply produced automatically?
