OL,3,CIs the BBC Red Button Text service
OL,4,Cserving a useful purpose?
OL,6,FIt is being killed off by stealth
OL,7,Fanyway. It is not supported by newer
OL,8,Fsatellite boxes and does not feature
OL,9,Fon cable.
OL,11,FIts main platform is Freeview.
OL,13,FI will always believe that the BBC
OL,14,Fneeds to be mindful of the digitally
OL,15,Fdisadvantaged and the vulnerable in a
OL,16,Fway that commercial broadcasters are
OL,17,Fnot.
